&lt;h2 id=&#34;oh-my-posh&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#oh-my-posh&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; oh-my-posh&lt;/h2&gt;
